			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Go to Act 3 -> Bhaal Temple.\r\n2) oe BTEnableAbduction\r\n3) Open Camp Debug book and add Laezel into camp.\r\n4) Go to camp or LongRest.\r\n5) Orin as Laezel with Yenna will appear in a Campfire Moment camp night.\r\n6) In the dialog with Orin-Laezel, do NOT provoke Orin to kill Yenna.\r\n7) Yenna survives after Orin leaves.\r\n8) Talk to Yenna."
				},
