				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Orin abductions Laezel. In the CFM, Orin-Laezel takes Yenna as hostage. Players could encourage Orin-Laezel to murder Yenna. But this dialog is when players spared her and talked to her after the encounter."
